- cs.AI is the most likely category as the paper is about implementing ethics in AI system development. 
- cs.CY (computers and society) is also likely as the paper discusses the ethical considerations of AI systems and their impact on stakeholders. 
- cs.SE (software engineering) is relevant as the paper discusses the need for methods and tools for implementing ethics in software development. 
- cs.HC (human-computer interaction) is relevant as the case study focuses on AI systems in the healthcare sector. 
- cs.RO (robotics) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses autonomous system failures and the need for ethical considerations in their development.
